{"text_id":169066,"tokens":["We"," propose"," a"," novel"," biologically","-","pla","u","sible"," solution"," to"," the"," credit"," assignment"," problem",","," being"," motivated"," by"," observations"," in"," the"," ventral"," visual"," pathway"," and"," trained"," deep"," neural"," networks","."," In"," both",","," representations"," of"," objects"," are"," built"," from"," parts"," and"," the"," overall"," representation"," is"," obtained"," by"," combining"," them","."," This"," solution"," is"," based"," on"," a"," two","-","stage"," architecture",","," where"," the"," first"," stage"," represents"," objects"," as"," parts"," and"," the"," second"," one"," combines"," these"," parts"," into"," an"," overall"," representation","."," We"," propose"," to"," use"," a"," biologically"," inspired"," local"," learning"," rule"," for"," the"," first"," stage",","," which"," is"," able"," to"," learn"," robust"," representations"," of"," parts","."," The"," second"," stage"," then"," combines"," these"," part","-","representations"," into"," object","-","representations"," in"," a"," supervised"," manner","."," We"," test"," our"," approach"," on"," an"," image"," recognition"," task"," and"," show"," that"," it"," out","performs"," other"," methods","."," In"," addition",","," we"," analyze"," the"," learned"," representations"," and"," show"," that"," they"," resemble"," those"," found"," in"," the"," ventral"," visual"," pathway","."," We"," discuss"," potential"," applications"," of"," our"," approach",","," such"," as"," in"," robotics"," or"," reinforcement"," learning","."],"sub_source":"sci_gen","model":"text-davinci-003","label":1}